biography_text: GONZALEZ, Anthony, a Representative from Ohio; born in Cleveland, Cuyahoga County, Ohio, September 19, 1984; graduated from Saint Ignatius High School, Cleveland, Ohio, 2003; attended The Ohio State University, Columbus, Ohio, 2003-2007; M.B.A., Stanford University, Stanford, Calif., 2014; professional athlete; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Sixteenth Congress (January 3, 2019-present).
